        <font color="white" face="Verdana" size="2"> I wish I knew!<img src=icon_smile.gif border=0 align=middle> I was told there are more and more necros soloing in PoG near the lake on my server.  Does anyone have any idea on how and what to hunt there.  Any input would be appreciated. Thanks!</P><P>Mephista Vex<BR>55 Defiler<BR>Saryrn</P><P> </font></td>

